PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_7422116\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_7422116\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 17, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104lvi1719409817744.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lvi1719409817744.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lvi1719409817744.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"kmc1665702640090\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      trigger Resized\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"kmc1665702640090__trigger_resized_397739\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The <code class=\"ph codeph\">Resized</code> trigger is fired when the parent form is started, and whenever the widget is resized (which is only possible if the Attach property is set).\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"kmc1665702640090__topic_d117869e1_d117870e1_d117871e1\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104lvi1719409817744_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"kmc1665702640090__codeblock_dwm_gfh_fcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger Resized\nparams\n   numeric widthPx : in\n   numeric heightPx : in\nendparams\n\n;your code here\n\nend ; Resized\n; -- end triggers for formcontainer widget</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"kmc1665702640090__section_w401ab1b7b5_w402ab1b7_w403ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"kmc1665702640090__table_d14636e1_d14637e1_d14638e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Applies to:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Form widgets: <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gev1665702640020.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gev1665702640020.html\" title=\"The ucontainer widget embeds a non-modal form in a field of the current form. Uniface provides a logical widget called FormContainer, which is mapped to ucontainer.\">ucontainer (FormContainer)</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gyf1688451219719.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gyf1688451219719.html\" title=\"The utabex widget enables users to navigate through a collection of contained forms by clicking a tab to display the form. The utabex widget is highly customizable, allowing extensive control over the appearance and behavior of the tabs. Uniface provides a logical widget called TabEx, which is mapped to utabex.\">utabex (TabEx)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Activation:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Activated on the target widget when the parent form is resized\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Default behavior:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n None\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Behavior upon completion:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n None\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kmc1665702640090__topic_d83937e1_d83938e1_d83939e1_d83940e1_d83941e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d610450e149\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kmc1665702640090__li_d44831e1_d44832e1_d44833e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword parmname\">widthPx</span>—width of the widget (without frame) in pixels\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kmc1665702640090__li_d44834e1_d44835e1_d44836e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword parmname\">heightPx</span>—height of the widget (without frame) in pixels\n </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kmc1665702640090__topic_d83942e1_d83943e1_d83944e1_d83945e1_d83946e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d610450e170\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kmc1665702640090__p_d117878e1_d117879e1_d117880e1\">If the parent widget of a contained form is attached to a form border and is resized, it may be necessary to change the contained form as well. For example, if the widget is becomes too small to display the contents of the contained form, you could display a different form.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kmc1665702640090__section_a2x_hfh_fcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d610450e180\">Example: Using the Resized Trigger </h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following ProcScript loads one of two forms in a Form Container,\n               depending on the available width.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"kmc1665702640090__pre_xvf_3fh_fcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger Resized\nparams\n numeric widthPx : in\n numeric heightPx : in\nendparams\n if (widthPx &gt; 300)\n ; Load form with wide layout in this Form Container\n @$fieldname = \"CUST_WIDE\"\n else\n ; Load form with narrow layout in this Form Container\n @$fieldname = \"CUST_NARROW\"\n endif\nend; Resized\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7422116\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7422116\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "trigger Resized Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 17, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 trigger Resized The Resized trigger is fired when the parent form is started, and whenever the widget is resized (which is only possible if the Attach property is set). Explain this code trigger Resized params numeric widthPx : in numeric heightPx : in endparams ;your code here end ; Resized ; -- end triggers for formcontainer widget Copy Applies to: Form widgets: ucontainer (FormContainer) , utabex (TabEx) Activation: Activated on the target widget when the parent form is resized Default behavior: None Behavior upon completion: None Parameters widthPx —width of the widget (without frame) in pixels heightPx —height of the widget (without frame) in pixels Description If the parent widget of a contained form is attached to a form border and is resized, it may be necessary to change the contained form as well. For example, if the widget is becomes too small to display the contents of the contained form, you could display a different form. Example: Using the Resized Trigger The following ProcScript loads one of two forms in a Form Container, depending on the available width. trigger Resized params numeric widthPx : in numeric heightPx : in endparams if (widthPx > 300) ; Load form with wide layout in this Form Container @$fieldname = \"CUST_WIDE\" else ; Load form with narrow layout in this Form Container @$fieldname = \"CUST_NARROW\" endif end; Resized Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}